⏺ Rate Limiter LLD — Complete Python Deep Dive

  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  What Are We Building?
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  API Gateway receives request from client_id="user_123" to endpoint="/search"                                                                                                                                
  Rate Limiter checks: "Has this user exceeded their quota?"                                                                                                                                                    
      → YES → reject, tell them when to retry                                                                                                                                                                   
      → NO  → allow, tell them how many requests remain                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
