  Step 5 — Token Bucket Algorithm (Deep Explanation)                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
  What is Token Bucket?
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Imagine a physical bucket that holds tokens (coins).
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Rules:                                                                                                                                                                                                      
    1. Bucket has a maximum capacity (e.g., 10 tokens)                                                                                                                                                          
    2. Starts full                                                                                                                                                                                            
    3. Each request takes 1 token                                                                                                                                                                               
    4. Tokens refill at a fixed rate (e.g., 1 token/second)
    5. If bucket empty → request denied                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
  Example: capacity=10, refill=1/second                                                                                                                                                                         
    t=0:    bucket has 10 tokens                                                                                                                                                                              
    t=0:    make 10 requests → bucket empty                                                                                                                                                                     
    t=0:    make 11th request → DENIED (bucket empty)                                                                                                                                                           
    t=1:    1 token refilled → make 1 request → allowed                                                                                                                                                         
    t=10:   10 tokens refilled → burst of 10 allowed again                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Why Use Token Bucket?                                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Allows BURSTS — a client can make many requests quickly                                                                                                                                                       
    (useful for search APIs, batch operations)                                                                                                                                                                  
  
  Maintains AVERAGE RATE — over time, can't exceed refill rate                                                                                                                                                  
    (protects your API from sustained abuse)                                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Used by: Stripe, AWS API Gateway, GitHub API                                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Per-Client State                                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
  Each client needs their own "bucket":

  @dataclass
  class TokenBucket:                                                                                                                                                                                            
      tokens: float          # current token count (float because partial tokens)
      last_refill_time: float  # when we last calculated tokens (unix timestamp in ms)                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Why float for tokens?                                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  # Scenario: refill_rate=1/sec, elapsed=500ms                                                                                                                                                                
  tokens_to_add = (500 * 1) / 1000 = 0.5 tokens                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  # If int: 0.5 → 0 (truncated) — refill never happens for < 1 second                                                                                                                                           
  # If float: 0.5 stored — accumulates correctly over time                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  # After another 500ms:                                                                                                                                                                                      
  tokens_to_add = 0.5 more                                                                                                                                                                                      
  total = 0.5 + 0.5 = 1.0  ← now we have a full token!                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Full Implementation with Step-by-Step Comments                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  import time                                                                                                                                                                                                 
  import math
  from dataclasses import dataclass                                                                                                                                                                             
  from typing import Dict
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  @dataclass                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  class TokenBucket:
      tokens: float
      last_refill_time: float

  class TokenBucketLimiter(Limiter):                                                                                                                                                                            
  
      def __init__(self, capacity: int, refill_rate_per_second: int):                                                                                                                                           
          self.capacity = capacity                    # max tokens (burst limit)                                                                                                                              
          self.refill_rate = refill_rate_per_second  # tokens added per second                                                                                                                                  
          self.buckets: Dict[str, TokenBucket] = {}  # per-client state                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
      def _get_or_create_bucket(self, key: str) -> TokenBucket:                                                                                                                                                 
          if key not in self.buckets:                                                                                                                                                                         
              # New client → starts with FULL bucket                                                                                                                                                            
              # last_refill_time = now (no refill needed yet)                                                                                                                                                   
              self.buckets[key] = TokenBucket(                                                                                                                                                                  
                  tokens=self.capacity,                                                                                                                                                                         
                  last_refill_time=self._now()                                                                                                                                                                  
              )                                                                                                                                                                                               
          return self.buckets[key]

      def _now(self) -> float:
          # Returns current time in MILLISECONDS
          # time.time() returns seconds, multiply by 1000 for ms                                                                                                                                                
          return time.time() * 1000
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
      def allow(self, key: str) -> RateLimitResult:                                                                                                                                                             
  
          # STEP 1: Get or create this client's bucket                                                                                                                                                          
          bucket = self._get_or_create_bucket(key)                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          # STEP 2: Calculate how many tokens have refilled since last request                                                                                                                                  
          now = self._now()                                                                                                                                                                                     
          elapsed_ms = now - bucket.last_refill_time                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
          # Convert elapsed time to tokens:                                                                                                                                                                     
          # elapsed_ms=1000, rate=10/sec → 10 tokens
          # elapsed_ms=500,  rate=10/sec → 5 tokens                                                                                                                                                             
          # elapsed_ms=100,  rate=10/sec → 1 token                                                                                                                                                            
          tokens_to_add = (elapsed_ms * self.refill_rate) / 1000                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
          # Add tokens but don't exceed capacity (bucket can't overflow)                                                                                                                                        
          bucket.tokens = min(self.capacity, bucket.tokens + tokens_to_add)                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          # Update last_refill_time to NOW                                                                                                                                                                    
          # Next request will calculate elapsed from this moment                                                                                                                                                
          bucket.last_refill_time = now                                                                                                                                                                         
  
          # STEP 3: Check if we have at least 1 token available                                                                                                                                                 
          if bucket.tokens >= 1:                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              # STEP 4a: ALLOW — consume 1 token                                                                                                                                                                
              bucket.tokens -= 1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              return RateLimitResult(                                                                                                                                                                         
                  allowed=True,
                  remaining=int(bucket.tokens),  # floor (don't show partial tokens)
                  retry_after_ms=None             # no retry needed                                                                                                                                             
              )                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          else:                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
              # STEP 4b: DENY — calculate when enough tokens will exist                                                                                                                                         
              # Need (1 - current_tokens) more tokens
              tokens_needed = 1 - bucket.tokens                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              # Time to accumulate those tokens:
              # tokens_needed=0.7, rate=10/sec → 0.7/10 sec = 0.07 sec = 70ms                                                                                                                                   
              # Math: tokens_needed / rate * 1000 (convert sec to ms)                                                                                                                                           
              retry_after_ms = math.ceil(                                                                                                                                                                       
                  (tokens_needed / self.refill_rate) * 1000                                                                                                                                                     
              )                                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
              return RateLimitResult(                                                                                                                                                                           
                  allowed=False,
                  remaining=0,                                                                                                                                                                                  
                  retry_after_ms=retry_after_ms                                                                                                                                                               
              )

