  Step 6 — Sliding Window Log Algorithm (Deep Explanation)                                                                                                                                                    
                                                          
  What is Sliding Window Log?
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Instead of tokens, track EXACT TIMESTAMPS of every request.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Rules:                                                                                                                                                                                                      
    1. Keep a queue of timestamps for each client                                                                                                                                                               
    2. When request arrives:                                                                                                                                                                                  
       a. Remove timestamps older than the window (they're expired)                                                                                                                                             
       b. Count remaining timestamps                                                                                                                                                                            
       c. If count < max_requests → allow, add current timestamp                                                                                                                                                
       d. If count >= max_requests → deny                                                                                                                                                                       
    3. Window is SLIDING — always "last N milliseconds"                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Example: maxRequests=3, window=60000ms (1 minute)                                                                                                                                                             
    10:00:00 → request → log=[10:00:00] → count=1 < 3 → ALLOW                                                                                                                                                   
    10:00:10 → request → log=[10:00:00, 10:00:10] → count=2 < 3 → ALLOW                                                                                                                                         
    10:00:20 → request → log=[10:00:00, 10:00:10, 10:00:20] → count=3 = 3 → ALLOW                                                                                                                               
    10:00:30 → request → count=3 already → DENY                                                                                                                                                                 
                retry_after_ms = 10:00:00 + 60s - 10:00:30 = 30 seconds                                                                                                                                         
    10:01:01 → request → 10:00:00 now expired (>60s ago)                                                                                                                                                        
                log=[10:00:10, 10:00:20] → count=2 < 3 → ALLOW                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Why Use Sliding Window Log?                                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  PERFECT accuracy — no approximation                                                                                                                                                                           
    Each request is counted in EXACTLY the window it belongs to
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Downside: memory                                                                                                                                                                                            
    Need to store every timestamp                                                                                                                                                                               
    Client making 1000 req/min → 1000 timestamps stored                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Use when: accuracy is critical, request rate is moderate                                                                                                                                                      
  Use Token Bucket when: bursts allowed, memory is concern                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Per-Client State                                                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  from collections import deque                                                                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  # deque = double-ended queue
  # O(1) append to right, O(1) remove from left                                                                                                                                                                 
  # Perfect for sliding window: add new timestamps to right,                                                                                                                                                    
  # remove old timestamps from left                                                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Why deque and not list?                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
  # list.pop(0) = O(n) — shifts all elements left
  # deque.popleft() = O(1) — pointer move only                                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  # With 1000 timestamps per client, 10k clients:                                                                                                                                                               
  # list:  10k × 1000 × O(n) = 10 billion operations per cleanup                                                                                                                                                
  # deque: 10k × 1000 × O(1) = 10 million operations per cleanup                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Full Implementation                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  from collections import deque                                                                                                                                                                               
  from dataclasses import dataclass, field
  from typing import Dict
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  @dataclass
  class RequestLog:                                                                                                                                                                                             
      # deque of timestamps (in milliseconds) of recent requests                                                                                                                                              
      # oldest at left (index 0), newest at right (index -1)                                                                                                                                                    
      timestamps: deque = field(default_factory=deque)                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  class SlidingWindowLogLimiter(Limiter):                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
      def __init__(self, max_requests: int, window_ms: int):                                                                                                                                                    
          self.max_requests = max_requests  # max allowed per window                                                                                                                                          
          self.window_ms = window_ms        # window size in milliseconds                                                                                                                                       
          self.logs: Dict[str, RequestLog] = {}  # per-client request history
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
      def _get_or_create_log(self, key: str) -> RequestLog:                                                                                                                                                   
          if key not in self.logs:                                                                                                                                                                              
              # New client → empty history                                                                                                                                                                    
              self.logs[key] = RequestLog()                                                                                                                                                                     
          return self.logs[key]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
      def _now(self) -> int:                                                                                                                                                                                  
          return int(time.time() * 1000)  # milliseconds
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
      def allow(self, key: str) -> RateLimitResult:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          # STEP 1: Get or create this client's request log                                                                                                                                                   
          log = self._get_or_create_log(key)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          now = self._now()
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          # STEP 2: Calculate cutoff — anything older than this is expired                                                                                                                                      
          # If window=60000ms and now=100000ms:
          # cutoff = 100000 - 60000 = 40000ms                                                                                                                                                                   
          # Any timestamp < 40000 is outside our window → remove it                                                                                                                                           
          cutoff = now - self.window_ms                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
          # STEP 3: Remove expired timestamps from the LEFT (oldest)                                                                                                                                            
          # deque: [old ... new]                                                                                                                                                                              
          # Keep removing from left while timestamp < cutoff                                                                                                                                                    
          while log.timestamps and log.timestamps[0] < cutoff:                                                                                                                                                
              log.timestamps.popleft()   # O(1)                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                              
          # STEP 4: Count remaining timestamps = requests in current window                                                                                                                                     
          current_count = len(log.timestamps)                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
          # STEP 5: Check if under the limit                                                                                                                                                                    
          if current_count < self.max_requests:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              # STEP 6a: ALLOW — record this request's timestamp                                                                                                                                              
              log.timestamps.append(now)  # add to right (newest)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              # remaining = how many more requests allowed                                                                                                                                                      
              # We just added one, so:                                                                                                                                                                          
              remaining = self.max_requests - len(log.timestamps)                                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              return RateLimitResult(
                  allowed=True,                                                                                                                                                                                 
                  remaining=remaining,                                                                                                                                                                        
                  retry_after_ms=None
              )

          else:

              # STEP 6b: DENY — calculate when oldest will expire                                                                                                                                               
              # oldest timestamp = log.timestamps[0] (leftmost)
              # It expires at: oldest + window_ms                                                                                                                                                               
              # Time until expiry: (oldest + window_ms) - now                                                                                                                                                 
              oldest = log.timestamps[0]                                                                                                                                                                        
              retry_after_ms = (oldest + self.window_ms) - now                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
              return RateLimitResult(                                                                                                                                                                           
                  allowed=False,
                  remaining=0,                                                                                                                                                                                  
                  retry_after_ms=retry_after_ms                                                                                                                                                               
              )

